{
  "stem": "15393.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 19.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, I ran and ran and ran.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know where I was running to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was just running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- [SIGHS] with the shopping, I can't remember did I drop the shopping, did I carry it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I really have a blank there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I knew where I found myself eventually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a sort of a place in Lwow where people used to go picnicking a lot for weekends.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so it was like a small hill out of which, when you were-- when you were on it, you saw the panoramic view of the city, which was very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it's a very well-known place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I ran up there, all the way up there, and hid among trees and bushes and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I just don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, how come that nobody saw me, that there was no one there?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in the middle of the week.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All right, maybe people weren't picnicking, but somebody must have seen such a person crazy running.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there I sat for hour-- what seemed like hours, like hours, because I wasn't going to go back in the daylight.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was waiting for night, really truly night, not just evening, night to fall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was-- must have been summertime, because it was-- took a long, long time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was not dressed warmly, dressed in my [INAUDIBLE] dress.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, it was summer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, I had to see that I get back before the main door is shut.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that it at 10 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, it wasn't, you know, really nighttime yet, but it was dark.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I began to make my descent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have never seen this man afterwards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, I never went-- never ventured out any more.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was my last escape.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
